data.description: Charming home featuring 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. With a beautiful backyard complete with a patio area, it offers a serene and inviting space for outdoor relaxation. The property boasts fresh paint, new flooring, and a unique and desirable floorplan, with an attached one stall garage and a newer concrete driveway and sidewalk.
